node.text:
Morning Routine for Success:

• Don’t check your phone for the first 8 minutes 📞 (whether you know it or not, your mood is being influenced by your phone. A stressful email, a person on insta who makes you feel a little more self conscious, some news article - you get the point)

• Think of 3+ things that you are grateful for and that make you happy. 🌞 (sounds silly but actually trains your mind to look for the good things not the bad) 

• Make your bed 🛏 (small accomplishments have a ripple effect)

• Drink a big glass of water💧(self explanatory)

• Meditate (can even be just 3mins to start with) 🧘‍♀️ 

• Brush your teeth with the opposite hand (it’s good for your brain!)
.
Set the intention that you’re going to have a happy day. Actively decide that when things arise you’re going to look for the positives in every situation. Because (as Shakespeare once said)
 “Nothing is either good or bad, but thinking makes it so” 😊 🌞 😊 🌞 🌞 🌞 ✨
